{"tid":1515210,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咩事呀你班人 篤灰制都玩得出？香港死緊啦","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T06:38:46.000Z","uid":5822,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e15c1746f5d80767f2ddc7e7019b316379e90bd3","tid":1515210,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"文革呢樣野比人屌足咁耐 就係篤灰 批鬥開始 <br />\n21世紀仲行返幾十年前既恥辱？你班人羞唔羞恥？<br />\n紀律部隊無紀律同咖哩魚蛋無咖哩有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n香港呢個咁文明既城市既然出現鼓勵篤灰呢個機制真係好諷刺 上一代打返黎 &ldquo;自由美譽 文化之都&rdquo;一次過比林鄭同班所謂執法者敗晒 香港無左外資就係nothing 你班所謂執法者人工一定變公安 以為而家逗緊既人工好正？無晒外資就睇你有咩技能搵工做<br />\n口口聲聲講外國勢力 無外國勢力你會唔會有咁既人工呀？<br />\n<br />\n成班垃圾個腦正係識yes sir thank you sir <br />\n真正當警察係使命既請你見到不公平既事要出聲 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敢出黎做勇武既係愛港第一人</span></span>唔夠愛香港既人唔會做得出連自己前途都唔要既事"},{"pid":"0ea32f0bfc08fae1683d1421fe3aeb80f5d093f8","tid":1515210,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"反佢啦！罷工啦！"},{"pid":"466e2ea787edc65d0c0504da5d304c736304a459","tid":1515210,"uid":28970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMA3SPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMA3SPa.jpg&h=ad1512a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUcRhfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUcRhfQ.jpg&h=71e75a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jn2559a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJn2559a.jpg&h=83039f49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28CmEua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28CmEua.jpg&h=40275ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGWKCfR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGWKCfR.jpg&h=c5ea8d69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USZHoVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https